It is the 28th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Geng Yin|ja|庚寅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and preceding {{ill|Ren Chen|ja|壬辰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Metal (Wu Xing)|ja|金|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Mao|ja|卯|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Wood (Wu Xing)|ja|木|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, creating a {{ill|Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|ja|相剋|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Metal overcomes Wood) relationship.
== Years of the Yin Metal Rabbit == Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 31 are considered Yin Metal Rabbit years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of the Yin Metal Rabbit''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | * [[31]] * [[91]] * [[151]] * [[211]] * [[271]] * [[331]] * [[391]] * [[451]] * [[511]] * [[571]] * [[631]] * [[691]] * [[751]] * [[811]] * [[871]] * [[931]] * [[991]] | * [[1051]] * [[1111]] * [[1171]] * [[1231]] * [[1291]] * [[1351]] * [[1411]] * [[1471]] * [[1531]] * [[1591]] * [[1651]] * [[1711]] * [[1771]] * [[1831]] * [[1891]] * [[1951]] | * [[2011]] * [[2071]] * [[2131]] * [[2191]] * [[2251]] * [[2311]] * [[2371]] * [[2431]] * [[2491]] * [[2551]] * [[2611]] * [[2671]] * [[2731]] * [[2791]] * [[2851]] * [[2911]] * [[2971]] |}
== Months of the Yin Metal Rabbit == In years where the last digit is 1 or 6 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the {{ill|February|ja|2月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of that year is considered a Yin Metal Rabbit month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|ja|啓蟄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Metal Rabbit == === Selection Days === Yin Metal Rabbit days are the 8th day of the {{ill|Jippōkure|ja|十方暮|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} cycle.
