{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Metal Rabbit|kanji=辛卯|romaji=kanoto usagi|onyomi=shinbō|p=xīmǎo|w=hsin-mao|mi=ɕin⁵³ mɑʊ̯|y=san1 maau5|j=san1 maau5|ci=sɐn maːu̯|mc=sin maw|oc-bs=sin maw|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Metal Rabbit''', also known as '''Shinbō''' (辛卯, Kanotō, Shinkin no Usagi, Shinkin no U, Shinbō), is one of the elements in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.
It is the 28th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Geng Yin|ja|庚寅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|Ren Chen|ja|壬辰|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Metal (Wu Xing)|ja|金|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|Mao|ja|卯|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|2=ja|3=卯|4=fr|5=Lapin (astrologie chinoise)|6=nl|7=Konijn (astrologie)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Wood (Wu Xing)|ja|木|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}, creating a {{ill|Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|ja|相剋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} (Metal overcomes Wood) relationship.
