{{infobox Chinese|l=Yin Metal Rabbit|kanji=辛卯|romaji=kanoto usagi|onyomi=shinbō|p=xīmǎo|w=hsin-mao|mi=ɕin⁵³ mɑʊ̯|y=san1 maau5|j=san1 maau5|ci=sɐn maːu̯|mc=sin maw|oc-bs=sin maw|qq=}} {{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}} '''Yin Metal Rabbit''', also known as '''Shinbō''' (辛卯, Kanotō, Shinkin no Usagi, Shinkin no U, Shinbō), is one of the elements in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.
It is the 28th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Geng Yin|ja|1=Yang Metal Tiger|2=ja|庚寅|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng Yin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Geng Yin|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Metal Tiger|qq=}} and preceding {{ill|Ren Chen|ja|1=Yang Water Dragon|2=ja|壬辰|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren Chen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren Chen|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Dragon|qq=}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Metal (Wu Xing)|ja|Metal (金)|1=Metal (wuxing)|ja|Metal (金)|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (金)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (Ngũ hành)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=Метал (У-сін)|lt=Metal (金)|lt=Metal (金)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (Ngũ hành)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=Метал (У-сін)|1=Metal (wuxing)|ja|Metal (金)|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (金)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (Ngũ hành)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=Метал (У-сін)|lt=Metal (金)|lt=Metal (金)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal (Wu Xing)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal (Wu Xing)|13=User:Immanuelle/Metal (wuxing)|ja|Metal (金)|1=Metal (wuxing)|lt=Metal (金)|2=es|3=Metal (Wu Xing)|4=it|5=Metallo (elemento)|6=vi|7=Kim (Ngũ hành)|8=tr|9=Metal (klasik element)|10=uk|11=Метал (У-сін)|lt=Metal (金)|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branch|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branch|qq=}} {{ill|Mao|ja|卯|1=Rabbit (Zodiac)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|2=ja|3=卯|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|2=ja|3=卯|4=fr|5=Lapin (astrologie chinoise)|6=nl|7=Konijn (astrologie)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mao|13=User:Immanuelle/Rabbit (zodiac)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mao|13=User:Immanuelle/Rabbit (Zodiac)|qq=}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Wood (Wu Xing)|ja|Wood (木)|1=Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|lt=Wood (木)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (Wu Xing)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (Wu Xing)|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (wuxing)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|2=uk|3=Дерево (елемент)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=Mộc (Ngũ hành)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=மரம் (சீன மெய்யியல்)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (木)|qq=}}, creating a {{ill|Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|ja|相剋|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Five Elements#Mutual overcoming|qq=}} (Metal overcomes Wood) relationship.
== Years of the Yin Metal Rabbit == Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 31 are considered Yin Metal Rabbit years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of the Yin Metal Rabbit''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | * [[31]] * [[91]] * [[151]] * [[211]] * [[271]] * [[331]] * [[391]] * [[451]] * [[511]] * [[571]] * [[631]] * [[691]] * [[751]] * [[811]] * [[871]] * [[931]] * [[991]] | * [[1051]] * [[1111]] * [[1171]] * [[1231]] * [[1291]] * [[1351]] * [[1411]] * [[1471]] * [[1531]] * [[1591]] * [[1651]] * [[1711]] * [[1771]] * [[1831]] * [[1891]] * [[1951]] | * [[2011]] * [[2071]] * [[2131]] * [[2191]] * [[2251]] * [[2311]] * [[2371]] * [[2431]] * [[2491]] * [[2551]] * [[2611]] * [[2671]] * [[2731]] * [[2791]] * [[2851]] * [[2911]] * [[2971]] |}
== Months of the Yin Metal Rabbit == In years where the last digit is 1 or 6 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stem|qq=}} {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the {{ill|February|ja|2月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/February|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/February|qq=}} of that year is considered a Yin Metal Rabbit month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|二十四節気|1=Solar term|2=ja|3=二十四節気|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Solar terms|qq=}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|ja|啓蟄|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jingzhe|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jingzhe|qq=}} to the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qingming|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Qingming|qq=}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Metal Rabbit == === Selection Days === Yin Metal Rabbit days are the 8th day of the {{ill|Jippōkure|ja|十方暮|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jippōkure|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jippōkure|qq=}} cycle.
